{
  "stem": "11723.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she wanted him to become a medical doctor, but my father didn't really want to be a medical doctor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And besides, he didn't want to go out of the country to go to a university, because at that time, there was a law in effect called numerus clausus, which meant that Jewish people were only a certain very small percentage of Jewish people could attend a university.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And depending on what connections they had, they could get into some, and they couldn't get into some others.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my uncle, for instance, my-- my father's brother, went to the University of Prague, because that's where he got accepted.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In Hungary, he couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father didn't want to leave the country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he went to the University of Economics, or-- I don't know how to translate it, because it's not an exact translation of a business university here.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, so he went into business with my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was very, very successful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when it came time to get married, he met my mother, who was a very beautiful woman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But she was already an old maid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was, I guess, 24 when they met.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And you know, in the 1930s, that was old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And my mother was not as educated as my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And as I mentioned earlier, she came from a very religious family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my grandfather on my mother's side was a grain merchant in Nyirbator, but he went bankrupt because his partner embezzled a great deal of money.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And his partner had, I think, six or seven kids.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my grandfather had to sell everything to bail out his partner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because otherwise, his partner would have gone to jail.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So they became very, very poor.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
